title: Battery Monitor [Jenu]
description:
Battery Monitor

Want to increase battery life of your laptop?

This tiny script is the ultimate solution.

Just copy this script and paste it to
"C:ProgramDataMicrosoftWindowsStart MenuProgramsStartup"

It will give a message as under whenever you are charging your laptop and the battery level reaches >95%. 

"Battery is at 96%"

Turn off the AC adapter after you get this message. It will increase your laptop battery life and also save the electricity
